<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	《周易参同契》注者储华谷考（一）
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">朱越利</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">读《道藏》读到《周易参同契》<font face="Times New Roman">3</font><font face="宋体">卷，看到署名储华谷注，无序跋，注文引张紫阳语。复检索该注之外的资料，因用力不够，故亦发现不多。于是，笔者初推断曰&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">华谷盖为北宋末或南宋初人</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">①</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">再推断曰储华谷<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">盖为北宋末或南宋时人</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">②</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一直不知道储华谷是何许人。近来翻检《四库全书》，无意中发现储华谷原来就是南宋诗人储泳。这样一来，笔者原来的两次推断，就可以修改得略微精确和肯定一些。并且，阅读新发现的这些资料，依稀可见储华谷身影。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">著《袪疑说》的南宋诗人储泳，字文卿，云间人。云间，今上海松江区。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">南宋陈起曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">泳，字文卿，云间人，著《华谷袪疑说》。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">③</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">元俞琰曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">储华谷《袪疑说》云：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">辟气为男，阖气为女。一阖一辟，男女攸分。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">④</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这段引文见于储泳《袪疑说》之《论男女之分生杀之炁》。宋末元初人丁易东撰《大衍索隐》卷<font face="Times New Roman">3</font><font face="宋体">引&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">云间储氏</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">论大衍之数，所引为储泳《易说》佚文。元俞琰撰《读易举要》卷</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">3</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">也引这段佚文，称&nbsp;<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">云间储华谷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。清初黄宗羲撰《易学象数论》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">6</font><font face="宋体">引</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">储华谷曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，所引是储泳《袪疑说》之《三刑是极数》一段。《钦定协纪辨方书》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">36</font><font face="宋体">《红沙》引储泳《袪疑说》之《六壬三杀乃先天四冲数》一段，按语曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">按</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">红沙</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">即身壬煞，储华谷以为极数。然驿马亦是极数，是不得以极为凶也。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">可知储泳亦被称为华谷、储华谷、云间储氏、云间储华谷等。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">清初<font face="Times New Roman">5</font><font face="宋体">种文献皆记载著《袪疑说》的南宋诗人储泳号华谷。朱彝尊撰《经义考》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">37</font><font face="宋体">曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">储氏《易说》，佚。丁易东曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">云间储氏，名泳。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">按：泳，号华谷，尝注《老子》，又有《祛疑说》。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">厉鹗《宋诗纪事》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">74</font><font face="宋体">曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">泳，字文卿，号华谷，云间人，著《华谷袪疑说》。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">《续文献通考》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">177</font><font face="宋体">曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">泳，字文卿，号华谷，侨居华亭，工于吟咏。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">查为仁、厉鹗《绝妙好词笺》卷</font><font face="Times New Roman">5</font><font face="宋体">曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">泳，字文乡，号华谷，云间人，著《华谷袪疑说》。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">文乡</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">应为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">文卿</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之误。《袪疑说》之《四库提要》曰：&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">泳，字文卿，号华谷，侨居华亭，工于吟咏。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑤</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">唯有清初《千顷堂书目》卷<font face="Times New Roman">12</font><font face="宋体">曰储泳&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">字华谷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，此当为</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">号华谷</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之误。是知储泳号华谷。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">注《周易参同契》的储华谷与号华谷并著《袪疑说》的南宋诗人储泳是否为同一人，还不能轻易认定，还需要确认《周易参同契注》与《袪疑说》等是否出自同一人。对照如下：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">1.&nbsp;<font face="宋体">储泳《胡定斋惠墨求诗》曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">万杵玄霜玉兔魂，刀圭炼就许平分。流珠轻滴银蟾露，化作催诗一片云。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑥</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这首诗的大意是：玉兔不停地用杵捣药那是明月之魂，（嫦娥）允诺将这些药炼成金丹后与我平分。金丹轻轻地滴落那是明月中的露珠，露珠化作催人赋诗的一片彩云。此诗表明诗人储泳熟悉丹经，向往内丹，也许就是在描写自己炼内丹。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">储泳《袪疑说》之《符印咒诀不灵祭将召邪》曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">符印咒诀，行持之文具也。精神运用，行持之玄妙也。感应乃其枝叶，炼养乃其根本。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">储泳以炼养为符咒之术的根本，而炼养包括内丹术。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同样，储华谷《周易参同契注》也是阐述内丹术的。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">2.&nbsp;<font face="宋体">储泳《祛疑说》之《阳神阴灵之说》曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">有客举倩女离魂话，因及张紫阳与雪窦禅师入定事。谓雪窦以禅定成至阴之爽，故不能持物而还，紫阳以金丹凝至阳之神，故能持果而返。此事之有无不必深辨，大概先辈以此别性宗与形神俱妙之功用不同耳。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">储泳说张伯端的理论以金为至阳。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同样，储华谷《周易参同契注》以金为纯乾。其曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">惟张紫阳深明此义，故有</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">八月十五玩蟾辉，正是金精壮盛时</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">之诗。且八月十五</font><font face="Times New Roman">&hellip;&hellip;</font><font face="宋体">金水盛满、药体纯乾之时也。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑦</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">纯乾即至阳。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">3.&nbsp;<font face="宋体">储泳《祛疑说》之《烧金炼银》曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">道家有金丹之说，故学者多以锻炼黄白为事。不知金丹者，人之真阳乃向上妙道，借谕为金。即禅宗之所谓金刚不坏身，取其不生不灭、永劫长存、具不漏之体也。丹者，乾为大赤，纯阳乾金故号为丹。岂徒以黄白为事！</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">储泳反对烧炼外丹，主张修炼内丹。他解释金丹之称，大意是说：真阳为金，金性坚固，故称</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">金</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">；纯阳为乾，乾为大赤，故称&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">丹</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同样，储华谷《周易参同契注》也说金为真阳，亘古不坏。其曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">坎中金为真阳之药，入离火炼之，亘古不坏，谕月之金精，受太阳符火，光明如常也。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同样，储华谷《周易参同契注》也说<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">丹</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">来自纯阳为乾，乾为大赤。其曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">及阴剥阳生，自坤化乾，乾为大赤。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&nbsp;&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">离中阴火本白，得铅则黄，火足丹成则变为赤色，即色转更为紫也。赤色通表里，乃乾为大赤之义。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑨</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">经对照可以看出，《周易参同契注》与《袪疑说》等理论相同，用语一致，出自同一人之手。可以确认，注《周易参同契》的储华谷与著《袪疑说》的南宋诗人储泳是同一人，储华谷即储泳。也就是说，《道藏》中《周易参同契》<font face="Times New Roman">3</font><font face="宋体">卷也是诗人储泳的作品，署名储华谷注是广义上的署名，实际署的是大号。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">二</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陈起《江湖后集》卷<font face="Times New Roman">11</font><font face="宋体">录储泳诗</font><font face="Times New Roman">22</font><font face="宋体">首。《江湖小集》和《江湖后集》之《四库提要》曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">陈起，字宗之，亦号陈道人，钱塘人。陈起能诗，凡江湖诗人俱与之善，开书肆于睦亲坊，刊《江湖集》以售。《江湖集》包括《江湖前集》、《江湖后集》、《江湖续集》、《中兴江湖集》等，南渡后诗家姓氏不显者，多赖是书以传，其摭拾之功亦不可没。宝庆初，陈起受史弥远迫害，《江湖集》板被劈，陈起被流放。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑩</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">黄韵静著《南宋出版家陈起研究》曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">陈起字宗之，号芸居，人称</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">陈道人</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">、</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">陈解元</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">，南宋临安府钱塘人，生卒年不详，至迟于宋孝宗淳熙十三年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1186&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">）出生，而约于宋理宗宝佑四年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1256&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">）去世，享年至少有七十岁。现存著作有《芸居乙稿》、《芸居遗诗》各一卷。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陈起《江湖后集》等没有记载储泳的生卒年。但陈起录储泳诗，表明储泳是南宋人。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">储泳有一位挚交卫宗武。张之翰《秋声集序》曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">公讳宗武，字淇父，官至朝请大夫，九山其自号。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">《秋声集》之《四库提要》曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">宗武，字淇父，自号九山，华亭人。淳祐间历官尚书郞，出知常州。罢归闲居三十余载，以诗文自娱。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>12</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">华亭即云间，即今上海松江区。卫宗武与储泳是同乡。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">卫宗武写有《挽储华谷四首》，无纪年。其第四首曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来才一见，病已不能支。拟作岁寒友，俄成夜壑悲。凄风吹老泪，落日照幽姿。赓唱无从再，酸心阅旧诗。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>13</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陶渊明作《归去来辞》曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归去来兮，田园将芜，胡不归？</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">卫宗武挽诗说</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，应指自己罢归。如同当今老干部说</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">退了</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">、</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">离了</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，意思自明。挽诗第四首前四句诗的大意是：我</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">后与储泳见过一面，那时储泳已经病体不支。我本打算将储泳作为退居生活中的伙伴，没想到才见一面就很快陷入与他永别的长痛。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">按人之常情，卫宗武致仕还乡后会很快与亲族故旧会见，盖很快去探视了卧病在床的挚交储泳。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">俄成夜壑悲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，说明探视后储泳很快即病故了。储泳盖病故于卫宗武</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的当年。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">至元甲午张之翰《秋声集序》曰：<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">始余为行台御史，道松江，会九山卫公洎其子谦，才一杯而别。后十年来牧是郡，访九山墓，宿草已六白矣。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">《秋声集》之《四库提要》据这段话断定卫宗武卒于至元己丑年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1289</font><font face="宋体">）。其曰：</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">据至元甲午张之翰所作集序称</font><font face="Times New Roman">&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">九山墓，宿草己六白</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font><font face="宋体">，则宗武实卒于至元二十六年己丑，在宋亡后十年。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">从卫宗武的卒年，可推测他<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">之年。从&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">淳祐间历官尚书郞，出知常州。罢归闲居三十余载</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&nbsp;</font><font face="宋体">看，卫宗武盖亦于淳祐间</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。如果其淳祐九年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1249</font><font face="宋体">）或更早</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，到至元二十六年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1289</font><font face="宋体">）去世，就应当说</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">闲居四十载</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">或</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">闲居四十余载</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">了。如果其淳祐十年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1250</font><font face="宋体">）或淳祐十一年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1251</font><font face="宋体">）</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，就应当说&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">闲居近四十载</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。《四库提要》没有使用这些用语。卫宗武于淳祐十二年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1252</font><font face="宋体">）</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的可能性最大，因为此年到去世之间前后闲居</font><font face="Times New Roman">37</font><font face="宋体">年，符合《四库提要》&nbsp;</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">闲居三十余载</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的用语。卫宗武淳祐十二年之后</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">归来</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">的可能性不大，因为下一年就改称宝祐元年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1253</font><font face="宋体">）了。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">储泳盖病故于淳祐十二年（<font face="Times New Roman">1252</font><font face="宋体">），距南宋亡国不足</font><font face="Times New Roman">30</font><font face="宋体">年。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">卫宗武《挽储华谷四首》之第三首说储泳&nbsp;<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">谈玄徒至老，养素竟成空</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。年过半百方可称老，未活到古稀之年则谈不上会养生。取半百至古稀年龄段正中的花甲之年，储泳盖享年</font><font face="Times New Roman">60</font><font face="宋体">岁左右，盖生于绍熙三年（</font><font face="Times New Roman">1192</font><font face="宋体">）。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">储泳当为南宋中后期人。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 附件 -->
	   		
		   		
			
	   </div>
   
   
   </td>
  </tr>
